-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
dojox.fx
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.1
Release date: 08/02/2007
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project state:
prototype / expermental
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Credits
	Peter Higgins (dante@dojotoolkit.org)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project description

	dojox.fx provides a class of animation effects
	to use.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	dojox.fx requires dojo (core) and the dojo.fx package
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Documentation

	existing API thus far:

	dojox.fx.sizeTo - size a node about it's center to a new width
	dojox.fx.addClass - animate the effects of applying a class to a node
	dojox.fx.removeClass - "   "    "    "   removing a class from a node


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	checkout dojox/fx* from SVN and place into your
	sibling dojox folder.

	see dojox/fx/tests/* for examples, and API tool for details.
	
	
